item.title: Pork Siomai
item.description: Siomai is the Philippines most popular dim sum. You can find it everywhere â€“ from the tiniest streets to the mega malls. Siomai is easily the fastest merienda or even an ulam option. It has the perfect combination of pork and spicy dip (saw-sawan). Siomai comes in different varieties and flavor mutations but we love the classic and simple pork siomai. Ingredients 1⁄2 kg ground pork 1 medium carrot, grated 1 medium.
